{"type": "article", "id": 61697, "title": "LV 新广告以「Humanoids」为主角，以及，这个华裔设计师用“自拍”展示新系列 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2019-03-04T09:01:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1580, "name": "巴黎时装周"}, {"id": 2326, "name": "Gap"}, {"id": 29000, "name": "Ted Baker"}, {"id": 57041, "name": "Yang Li"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/201903031931453RdSagDJwCksm6Tt.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/anya-hindmarch-up-for-sale\" rel=\"nofollow\">英国设计师品牌 Anya Hindmarch 或被出售</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 根据 BoF 报道，曾因童趣手袋走红的独立设计师品牌 Anya Hindmarch 可能会被出售。卡塔尔私募基金 Mayhoola 于 2012 年收购该品牌，并将股份从 2012 年的 39.9% 升至 2018 年的 75%，去年 9 月最后一次注资时花了 2000 万英镑。但 2017 年，Anya Hindmarch 税前亏损已高达 2820 万英镑。&nbsp;</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.usatoday.com/story/money/business/2019/03/03/gymboree-which-has-filed-bankruptcy-sell-its-gymboree-and-crazy-8-brand-childrens-place-and-its-jani/3049235002/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gap 集团收购美国高端童装品牌 Janie and Jack</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Gap 集团于 3 月 1 日与 Gymboree（金宝贝）达成协议，将以 3500 万美元收购 Janie and Jack。收购包括品牌、库存、门店，以及与金宝贝相关的品牌、网站和知识产权。金宝贝于今年 1 月申请破产保护，运营有 900 家门店，其中 Janie and Jack 拥有 102 家门店及 45 家工厂店。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Ted-Baker-CEO-quits-packs-his-bags-with-immediate-effect,1074658.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ted Baker CEO 在行为不端指控后离职</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Ted Baker CEO&nbsp;Ray Kelvin 去年 12 月被指控在工作场合有不端行为，包括“强制性拥抱”等。Ted Baker 随后雇佣 Herbert Smith Freehills LLP 律所展开调查，而 Ray Kelvin 则自愿停职配合调查。3 月 4 日，Ray Kelvin 主动辞职，但否认了一切指控。代理 CEO Lindsay Page 将继续代为运营公司，而董事局主席 David Bernstein 则将提供额外支持。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://fashionunited.uk/news/people/chanel-announces-additional-karl-lagerfeld-successor/2019030141904\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chanel 任命又一位“老佛爷”继任者</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 根据 Vogue 报道，除 Chanel 创意工作室总监 Virginie Viard 将接替 Karl Lagerfeld 担任品牌创意总监外，Eric Pfrunder 将担任 Chanel 精品部形象总监。Eric Prunder 于 1983 年加入香奈儿，30 多年来与 Virginie Viard 一同协助 Karl Lagerfeld 工作。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.nssmag.com/it/reportage/17856/humanoids-milan-louis-vuitton\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>NSS Magazine</em> 为&nbsp;Louis Vuitton 2019 春夏系列制作了一部以「Humanoids」为主题的造型特辑。</a></strong><br></p><p>在这个特辑中，<em>NSS Magazine </em>想象星际游客来到地球上，试图发现这里最美风景，但身上只背了旅行包。“星际游客”形象的未来感与熟悉的旅游胜地融合在一起，带来一种陌生又熟悉的浪漫。</p><p>艺术总监：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vinceskiopps/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vincenzo Schioppa</a><strong>；造型师：</strong><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/casiraghifrancesca/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Francesca Casiraghi</a><strong>。</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105423VkYjU98nwQ5xugGs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105429JmlS3rjxZUDoCiuF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903041054184rICSMJzYalpQWT8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105417ju89Hd4Cqltn5kXS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105417RmfBuPyDVTHrbIog.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105418fdCB3WPXNhGcwLvz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105417tEip0Qfzek8qvPMd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105419uAIlwLXm57iK2JQY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903041054206mVlOX3uDrWZ70wf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105420SyrdKspieb79NgOC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105420m3wGnRvIVp9JNiSg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105421kQXxzrUn75NbD8Hy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105421w8NoyJb5c1avC049.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105427XNz5fgyEIZ69C3Sc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105421Ap7MR3VPS1gnZjNy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105422Frg5pIG849lnf0Vy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105422TJYIc4A8BaX0oyds.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105422cMVkLma9hNbRKflQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903041054237H2F0lOpSamu8ytV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304105423gHUxEImbDkir2WvM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/43541/1/stoya-rossy-de-palma-jehnny-beth-yang-li-aw19-pfw-paris-fashion-week\" rel=\"nofollow\">华裔设计师李阳的伦敦独立品牌 Yang Li 发布 2019 秋冬系列。</a></strong></p><p>系列的发布手法挺有趣。李阳没有采用传统的走秀（show）、时装演示（presentation）或 Lookbook 形式，而是找来英国摇滚乐队 Savages 主唱 Jehnny Beth（她也作过 Gucci 秀场模特）、歌手兼作家 Stoya、西班牙演员 Rossy de Palma、瑞士演员&nbsp;Aomi Muyock 等人，请他们从系列中选出一两件穿上，自己用喜欢的方式自拍。</p><p>“他们个性不同，但共性却是为个人主义感到骄傲。他们的力量也来源于此。除了他们的脸我还想展现更多东西。我们生活在一个控制个人形象比什么都重要的时代，在时尚行业就更是如此。我希望能放弃这种控制，让模特们放手去做，创造一个真实的故事时刻。”李阳<a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/43541/1/stoya-rossy-de-palma-jehnny-beth-yang-li-aw19-pfw-paris-fashion-week\" rel=\"nofollow\">在接受 <em>Dazed</em> 采访时说</a>。他认为收回的影像就像圣诞节早上拆礼物那样令人惊喜。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135650jTpWCE5PtD7LSws3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135649slOxt7k6YaiIPWjz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135649sHfckUON7QLu2El1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135650XKCGn8NgB9pR3tQ2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903041356492blQTJUSZCINXxPz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135650jcMU6BtJaP9WNsDl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135655aIP97Qvg8pwyNDfV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135651MLTBonK5S3t9Hpwr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135652x3UvXY6P4CaBwz0J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135652fCAXbSRqcVmLy4xz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135653GAcYQHFg5q1xO9e2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903041356543wzgOFyP9kfbAGTM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135655h73qfPropm91LkYR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135656f9d0BDoOq3tZVsL8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304135707su2cBnLxFybQkWr9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>巴黎时装周继续。</strong></p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/paris/celine/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Celine 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>Hedi Slimane 的新系列有些出人意料，又在情理之中。你仍然可以看到 Saint Laurent 时期的影响，如紧身裤、短裙、大量黑色的使用，不过模特们看上去不再叛逆而颓废。人们熟悉那种自信、平静的 Celine 又回来了。</p><p>贯穿始终的造型是：一件宽大、有点男性的外套，一件舒适的半裙，长皮靴，羊毛衫或衬衫，再加一套花色围巾或长项链。WWD 将其概括为”法式中产“风格。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140604wqX16ImFUPvDJ9zM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140602nwkRcLgQVNXM645r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140603fHi7Tj96zwkphRVa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140603gbHoxIyB2GTenpJS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140605vLCgptkM5d3e2Yzq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903041406059oyxjOulbQaqw8eB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140605ZujhgaSEP75T81ql.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140608S6YMCZi4FXh3yIav.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140608hlf6CN7eKE0oDvZ1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140609A8nx0493Uwe5PXR7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140611ZhLKem2Tcrpg5wVF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140609BIcTUfx2LHg7pmFb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140611Ai2WFIa4UrOy1VbY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140611ELfBoS3QalhTVDIc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/paris/loewe/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Loewe 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>秀场选在了巴黎联合国教课文组织总部内，铺着黑色人字形木地板，白色墙壁上悬挂着一系列可追溯至 16 -17 世的绅士淑女们的椭圆微型肖像。</p><p>创意总监 Jonathan Anderson 说他想在这一季做减法，在简洁、轻松的同时又不舍弃品牌原有的艺术性和浪漫感，所以这些从远处看挺简洁的造型拉近看都充满细节。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140838n5XhwxETMZ3vskHd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140838TUkzBSfu37iZ8vyd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190304140838JV9KxW5tACog1Hrv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.